    "Everything seemed to be going according to plan.",
    "However, despite Max's caution and thorough preparations, a feeling of unease began to creep in.",
    "There was something off about the atmosphere in the room.",
    "Unbeknownst to Max, a double agent within their own agency had betrayed them.",
    "This agent, corrupted by the Phoenix organization, had tipped off the leaders about the surveillance devices."
